attachment.heading: 2021 Edition Recodification Table
attachment.text: This table shows the location of former Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Code sections within the 2021 Edition of the code.
To find where a new chapter or section is located, type the old chapter name or number, or old section number into the box below.
